header.name: Bloodfire Palace
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: After being destroyed in a terrible battle a millenium ago the palace remained uninhabited. Recently a party of bandits rediscovered it.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A rear entrance into the palace.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: An uncanny, unnaturally heavy object in a glass trophy case.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: A tome of invocation on a pedestal table.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A basket holds some gold and a blood-stained hammer.

game_elements.name: Item 5
game_elements.description: A cape hidden in a crack of the wall.

game_elements.name: Item 6
game_elements.description: A mosaic of a seashell pattern on the ceiling

game_elements.name: Item 7
game_elements.description: A lavishly decorated door with a keyhole on the eastern wall of the large room.

game_elements.name: Item 8
game_elements.description: A broken chest with gems in it.

game_elements.name: Item 9
game_elements.description: A dying halfling, a key among his belongings.
